## Output: /packages/tokens, /packages/ui, brand style documentation.

## Example Usage
``
/DATABASE 为 {{PROJECT}} 设计表/索引/RLS。实体：{{SCHEMA_HINT}}。支持向量检索（pgvector），并写插入/检索示例。
```

## Key Outputs
- supabase/migrations/*.sql (tables, indexes, triggers, RLS)
- functions/ (optional: stored procedures/Edge Functions)
- scripts/seed.ts (seed data)
- Authentication and multi-tenant policies (using auth.uid() to control row-level access)